{"tid":1833457,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重推代post] 一個台灣人想對香港人說的話","createTime":"2020-01-22T01:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T03:12:19.000Z","uid":102225,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"665ca0d5fc170cbcee8b9d5e2b7534cba4afb295","tid":1833457,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T01:59:49.000Z","msg":"台灣朋友交托我幫手出post，大家都幫幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------<br />\n大家好，我是一個台灣人。想在這裡跟香港的你們說一些話，所以就借了朋友的連登ac。<br />\n我一直很喜歡香港，會聽會說廣東話，都是從港產片和廣東歌中學的。我去過香港旅遊，在616的時候也來過香港，跟你們一起遊行。我好想好想再去香港，但遺憾的因為我可能已不能再入境了，因為我害怕，在運動的前期已經有台灣的社運人士被消失了近一個月，後來得知是去香港的時候被抓去中國，因為「分裂國家」，現在還沒有放出來。<br />\n<br />\n現在我只能盡自己能做的，在台灣的街上貼網路文宣組做的文宣，有些香港人或是知情的台灣人會來跟我說一些很可怕的事，一直哭一直哭。<br />\n<br />\n大選我們贏了，晚上從家鄉跑回蔡英文競選總部聲援香港人，沒有你們，我們可能沒辦法贏的。<br />\n很感謝很感謝你們的幫助，看到現場有很多的香港人特意過來台灣只為支持我們，這份情意我們會謹記，絕不忘記。<br />\n<br />\n追求自由和民主的道路是很漫長又艱辛的，但願黎明快來到。<br />\n想分享一首害我一直哭的歌給你們聽，是連登巴打重新填詞的暴徒，令我想起台灣的一部關於太陽花學運記錄片《暴民》，部分裏面發生的事情跟香港這次運動所出現的狀況有點類似。<br />\n我們都不是暴民暴徒，只是愛自己城市的人而己。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我不能代表每一位台灣人，但我是絕對支持香港人的。<br />\n<br />\n你們真的厲害，加油。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q6QRVWTyrYg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq6QRVWTyrYg&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmNw%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=b93a8cc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q6QRVWTyrYg</a>"},{"pid":"2d2d39b3f4b8606069da2b0d3967cc50cae3a303","tid":1833457,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:05:19.000Z","msg":"[重推代post]推(1/10)"},{"pid":"8c39c628ba35da8ad6461064aacaabc1cf39ef31","tid":1833457,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7941da21a9fb90e0acd9a3071e27c6d5cf3d86b","tid":1833457,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:07:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e72d31c9fa89e48014ad41060dffd032f3163b40","tid":1833457,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:27:36.000Z","msg":"[重推代post]推(2/10)"},{"pid":"80775b3ece4a68837c9fb89ee3879c06fc6b9d9d","tid":1833457,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:28:22.000Z","msg":"[重推代post]推(3/10)"},{"pid":"f62728e1b9529c327f56651bce9e4fbac799be15","tid":1833457,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:57:24.000Z","msg":"[重推代post]推(4/10)"},{"pid":"0e6a6da9886b49b8ba47a453282609ed03d2643c","tid":1833457,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"[重推代post]推(5/10)"},{"pid":"a174661a598a841e2a4b19336b64e005c7534a68","tid":1833457,"uid":85457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T12:54:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8303776e7b7b6188ff65a99bbe980de168a8632f","tid":1833457,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:36:48.000Z","msg":"[重推代post]推(6/10)"},{"pid":"15ff1fb67fc3e26c26500bb4429016f31d74c8d9","tid":1833457,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"[重推代post]推(7/10)"},{"pid":"bdc6ef3d78fc93b93bdc296b2c1b2d9e52ff6704","tid":1833457,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"[重推代post]推(8/10)"},{"pid":"f994b0e330f22b77ee47432579d7f23c4d6d600b","tid":1833457,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f142f90696c18298b24ecc3f29803d44a7a2ef9","tid":1833457,"uid":14816,"l